# Changelog

## [0.5.0] - 2019-10-07

### Changed
- use libKitsuneCommon 0.6.0
- update includes for new style
- made logger easier with simple define-makros


## [0.4.1] - 2019-09-15

### Fixed
- build-script had always used the newest, but not the correct version of libKitsuneCommon


## [0.4.0] - 2019-09-14

### Changed
- update logger-interface for eaiser handling
- unbind data-buffer from the binary-files


## [0.3.0] - 2019-09-08

### Added
- support for sqlite3-database
- simple event logger

### fixed
- updateFileSize-method in binary-files had not updated the number of blocks
- blocksize of binary-files could differ from the data-buffer


## [0.2.1] - 2019-08-27

### Added
- user-documentation

### Changed
- update for using libKitsuneCommon 0.4.x
- update comments in files


## [0.2.0] - 2019-08-17

### Changed
- changed file-names for better readable


## [0.1.0] - 2019-08-03

### Added
- support test-files
- support binary-files
